text: Carolina Colorado Henao (born September 7, 1987 in Caldas, Antioquia, Colombia) Colorado's bio page connected to the 2008 Colombia Olympic team, from the Colombia's Institute of Sport (COLDEPORTES); retrieved 2010-04-14. is an Olympic and national record-holding swimmer from Colombia.
